description: Contains helper functions for serializing and deserializing Note objects to and from JSON format.

methods.name: noteToJsonMap
methods.description: Converts a Note object to a JSON-serializable Map.

methods.name: noteFromJsonMap
methods.description: Creates a Note object from a JSON Map.

methods.name: noteToJsonString
methods.description: Encodes a Note object into a JSON string.

methods.name: noteFromJsonString
methods.description: Decodes a JSON string into a Note object.

methods.name: notesListToJsonString
methods.description: Encodes a list of Notes into a JSON string.

methods.name: notesListFromJsonString
methods.description: Decodes a JSON string into a list of Notes.
